title: 12 pounds of meth, heroin seized in raid of Alabama drug trafficking organization
text:
Published By: Al.com: Mobile - Today 
Law enforcement seized 12 pounds of methamphetamine, one pound of heroin and three guns during a raid of a Chickasaw residence on Oct. 6....
